DarkMouse::

She stood in the doorway and kept watch. She looked at Koj, she still 
kind of wanted to see is she could kick his tail. She was feeling 
auwnry and wanted some action. She knew she couldn't pick a fight, 
but she was kind of hoping he'd make a move.
